Findings.Message: Despite what everyone tells you, it is a HUGE mistake to use the PDF format for your resume.
A street level address was not found in the contact information. A full contact address should always be included in a resume as it allows for location based searches.
We found no work history positions within the past year. A resume should include work history information, including time off, for the most recent year.

It is a almost always a bad idea to list jobs which ended more than ten years. ago. (1) They aren't very relevant or important compared to your more recent experience, and (2) They can be used (consciously or subconsciously) by recruiters and software to practice age discrimination.
